thread.title: Deb Hayes

author: Deb Hayes
title: Deb Hayes
text:
1 Duer Place Cherrybrook NSW 2126
The Open Agent Service is great service as it gives you all the information you need too make an informed decision as to what Agent you should interview to sell your home. A very good service.
The only criticism I have is when we were negotiating the final sell price with the Agent they used Open Agent as a negative as they had to pay Open Agent a 20%? commission.
